1 A BILL for an Act to create and enact a new chapter to title 15 of the North Dakota Century
2 Code, relating to the creation of the army forces reserve component scholarship program.
3 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
4 SECTION 1. A new chapter to title 15 of the North Dakota Century Code is created and
5 enacted as follows:
6 Definitions.
7 For purposes of this chapter:
8 1. "Active duty" means full-time service pursuant to an executive order of the president of
9 the United States or the governor or an act of the congress of the United States.
10 2. "Institution of higher education" means an institution at which the applicant is enrolled
11 in:
12 a. A degree-granting program, whether the institution is under the control of the
13 state board of higher education or privately controlled;
14 b. An in - state nursing education program approved by the North Dakota board o f
15 nursing; or
16 c. A program for a high - demand occupation identified under subsection 3 of section
17 15 - 10 - 38.1 .
18 Army forces reserve component scholarship program - State board of higher
19 education.
20 1. The state board of higher education shall:
21 a. Administer the army forces reserve component scholarship program.
22 b. Approve all eligible applicants.
23 c. Process applications for the scholarship in the order received.
24 d. Provide scholarships regardless of the financial need of the applicant.
